# WhisperX Configuration
# API + Swagger UI: https://whisperx.internal/docs

# HuggingFace token — REQUIRED for speaker diarization (pyannote models).
# 1. Create a token: https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
# 2. Accept the gated model terms (once, while logged in):
#      https://huggingface.co/pyannote/speaker-diarization-3.1
#      https://huggingface.co/pyannote/segmentation-3.0
# Without this, transcription still works but diarization fails.
WHISPERX_HF_TOKEN=EXIST_CLI
